<h4>Site Analytics</h4>
M.E. will not route customer web server traffic through third party analytics products.
<br><br>
M.E. will analyze its own web server traffic to determine how customers are interacting with M.E. products.
<br><br>
M.E. will use the IP address sent to all web servers by web browsers to determine which regions of the Earth customers are using our products from. Customer IP addresses will not be stored after the above process is completed, for each web request. A record correlating customers and customer IP addresses will never exist within the M.E. infrastructure.